News.headline: Dagenham & Redbridge Poppy Appeal 2016
News.short_description: Dagenham & Redbridge raised a total of £759.01 for the local Royal British Legion Poppy Appeal
News.description:
Thank you to everyone who donated to our Poppy Appeal on the 12th November at our home fixture against Gateshead, we managed to raise a grand total of £759.01 for the local Royal British Legion Poppy Appeal.

A special mention goes to the Banks family who donated an outstanding £205.01 in our charity auction for our limited edition signed Remembrance Day signed shirt, in which the club are extremely grateful for.
